\n<br />\n所有行動都要有目的<br />\n<br />\n例如掟磗既動作係想傷害警犬<br />\n但磗其實扣唔到防暴血 係無效攻擊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對唔係叫大家使用真正既攻擊性武器</span></span></strong><br />\n但冇有效攻擊手段既時候<br />\n係咪寧願唔對峙唔比機會黑警拉人呢<br />\n<br />\n我明大家好撚嬲 但嬲之餘要諗下點先達到目的 <br />\n不過一定唔係盾 同火燒垃圾車<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對唔係叫大家使用真正既攻擊性武器</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尊重前線<br />\n但盲撐只會變成教條<br />\n<br />\n利申只係一個偶爾既盾兵"},{"pid":"587fd0760cacf2504d6a2a2842dfc383861126ed","tid":1481198,"uid":132792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"d前線付出左生命抗戰 係英雄<br />\n佢地唔割和理非已經好仁慈 所以唔該d和理非俾前線屌兩句就硬食忍下"},{"pid":"6ec15c36fe1fcdb3336f67731c68c58272bccd0b","tid":1481198,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fbf0d1ec658a5416decd406b4fac35aa4876ac","tid":1481198,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8d8fcbe296e86aa2b4e7072181b6e0f22fb4cb","tid":1481198,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2680b53ecf0496552ea1524da8001115967ff955","tid":1481198,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T00:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584563b7da92d2d9b07b0b3b5d358b49cb3acb34","tid":1481198,"uid":289775,"like":0,"dislik